
  Silcoon    Bug Type Pokémon

  SILCOON tethers itself to a 
  tree branch using silk to keep 
  from falling.  There,  Silcoon 
  hangs quietly while it awaits 
  evolution.  It peers out of the 
  silk cocoon through a small hole. 
  
	   Evolution Chain
  Wurmple ► Silcoon ► Beautifly

Stage 2 Forms:
  silcoon
  cascoon

Stage 3 Forms:
  beautifly
  dustox

